          <span class="font-body font-semibold text-[16px] text-[#0a0a0a] leading-[110%]" style="height:18px;">#1 Describe your app</span>
          <div class="hiw-step-desc transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden" style="max-height:42px;opacity:1;">
            <p class="font-body font-normal text-[14px] text-[#525252] leading-[150%] mt-1" style="width:504px;height:42px;">Tell Appnigma what you're building in plain English. Objects, flows, Lightning components, Apex — no spec doc or schemas required.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2: Review inside your CRM (inactive, 80px) -->
